Remarks. The type locality of Ighibirei is in Central province on the Kemp Welch river (
Helgen et al. 2008
). In the absence of knowledge of this locality specimens were assigned to this species (see Ballantyne and McLean 1970 ; Ballantyne 1987a ). Any reassessment of such specimens can only be made on morphological grounds.
